author: GameSpot
description:
Based on the hit video game series, 'Fallout' returns for Season 2 on Prime Video on December 17. Cast members Kyle McLachlan (Hank MacLean), Walton Goggins (The Ghoul), Aaron Moten (Maximus), Moisés Ariass (Norm MacLean), Frances Turner (Barb Howard) and Macaulay Culkin (Caeser's Legion), along with showrunners Jonthan Nolan and Geneva Robertson-Dworet reveal how they would respond to some of the wackier decisions the player character is faced with in 'Fallout: New Vegas'.

#falloutseason2 #fallout #falloutseries
title: The 'Fallout' Season 2 Cast Make BRUTAL Decisions in 'Fallout: New Vegas'
